    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <description>Join record inserted by the LoggerNotificationProcessor runtime each time a record matches a LoggerNotificationRule__c rule. The matched record's ID + SObject type are always stored in the generic MatchedRecordId__c / MatchedSObjectType__c fields, and additionally in a typed Lookup (LogEntry__c, Log__c, LoggerScenario__c, LogEntryTag__c) when the source SObject type has one. Powers the Total Matches rollup on the rule and the threshold-over-time count queries.</description>
